{"tid":1581734,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到呢刻仲專登寫fake news嘅手足，可唔可以停低思考一下fake news嘅作用係咩","createTime":"2019-09-19T16:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T15:30:14.000Z","uid":159913,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"289e1870232fddb279e8aff73c39159bb81e3702","tid":1581734,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>1. 想佔領道德高地? </strong><br />\n6.12、7.21、8.31之後我哋嘅道德力量已經大到不得了，散播fake news只會損害一直累積落嚟嘅基礎<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. Fake news可以嘩眾取寵，爭取民意支持?</strong><br />\n其實大部份民眾唔會跟得好貼，fake news未必reach到大部份人，但相反會令運動嘅積極份子越嚟越脫離群眾，行上掘頭路<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 對家用fake news，點解我哋要有政治潔癖?</strong><br />\n唔係政治潔癖嘅問題，呢幾個月勇武升級得到廣泛支持證明香港人潔癖已慢慢減退<br />\n但事實係抗爭者冇大台，先天上就容易出現資訊混亂<br />\n而中共、港共政府、甚至何君堯facebook page都係佢哋大台，溝通渠道單向清晰(雖然啲人劣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n你針對抗爭者散播fake news，越「成功」就越令抗爭者不知所措<br />\n做得黃絲多數有返啲批判性思考，冇咁容易照單全收，最後陷入半信半疑嘅狀態<br />\n<br />\n我唔相信所有fake news都係對家惡意散播嘅，因為呢種暗黑兵法嘅後果難以控制<br />\n如果係同路人嘅話我想你諗諗fake news嘅作用同呢幾日對運動行動嘅影響<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>總結：如果要玩fake news，請target對面，放過自己友啦<br />\n唔好幫政府將「五大訴求」主線失焦啦，好冇?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n【死全家系列】紅磡站跳軌一事可見有大量人惡意散發FAKE NEWS<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581609</a><br />\n<br />\nFact Check模式統一化提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576054</a>"},{"pid":"56fd42db41ae6e337dcf608eddd9ec2643d54ac5","tid":1581734,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=aa352e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"12aadf1f83e5eb941a051e2f6fedf12ee6d68bb5","tid":1581734,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/tx75ett.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n（有圖）簡單一張圖話你知來緊會發生咩事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581212</a><br />\n<br />\n時間用嚟做實事好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac190f4cd51caff7f07fabb117dcdbd4a633341","tid":1581734,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:48:27.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"882bc8d99fba0a0345a9dee33c1fe00c6a8dc80d","tid":1581734,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb572b72a44d6426c6291cee7fa09d275a4c270","tid":1581734,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ac190f4cd51caff7f07fabb117dcdbd4a633341","tid":1581734,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:48:27.000Z","msg":"認同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji